summary:
### **Exploration Results Summary (Dynasty Gold Project)**  

- **High-grade gold-silver mineralization confirmed from surface at Cerro Verde**:  
  - 4.5m @ 3.2 g/t Au, 3.5 g/t Ag (CVC25-122)  
  - 6.2m @ 2.0 g/t Au, 20.2 g/t Ag (CVC25-104)  
  - 6.4m @ 2.3 g/t Au, 12.1 g/t Ag (CVT25-009)  
  - 12.6m @ 1.2 g/t Au, 13.0 g/t Ag (CVT25-010)  

- **Extensional results outside current resources**:  
  - 12.0m @ 0.8 g/t Au, 4.7 g/t Ag (CVT25-011)  
  - 2.8m @ 3.0 g/t Au, 2.5 g/t Ag (CVT25-016)  

- **Resource update expected in late Q3 2025**:  
  - Ongoing drilling (two diamond rigs active, 6,000m program).  
  - Cerro Verde hosts 1.9Moz of Dynasty's 3.1Moz gold resource.  

- **Mobile magneto-telluric (MMT) survey completed**:  
  - Covers 9km epithermal gold & porphyry copper corridor for future targeting.  

*No capital markets activity or financial impacts identified—operational update only.*
